quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,"Ne bakanile imbakha nobachelasilia Abandu bolukongo, olwa betselwa nende Abarumwa."
  36,14,"Olwa khwabarumila babili, nibabakatsula mana nikhubametela owakhataru. Nibaboola mbu: “Toto efwe khurumilwe khwinywe.”"
  36,15,"Nibaboola mbu: “Enywe mulisa Abandu shinga efwe, ne (Nyasaye) Omunji Wetsimbabaasi shiyeshiakhwo shiosishiosi tawe, ne enywe mukatinjia butswa.”"
  36,16,"Baboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi amanyile mbu efwe toto khurumilwe khwinywe."
  36,17,"Ne khubula elindi tawe halali okhusia khuli habulafu.”"
  36,18,"Baboola mbu: “Efwe toto khulolanga lisubiro khwinywe. Nimulalekhana ninafu tawe, toto khulabalasa amachina, ne toto mulanyoolwa nende eshinyasio eshikhongo okhurula khwifwe.”"
  36,19,"Baboola mbu: “Lisubiro lwenyu lili khwinywe. Khulwa sa mbu mwitsulisibwe? Halali enywe muli sa abandu babura eshichelo?”"
  36,20,"Mana omusatsa mulala niyetsa okhurula mumbeka wolukongo olo nayuukanga muno, naboola mbu: “Enywe abandu banje, loonde Abarumwa bano."
  36,21,"Loonde balia abalabasabanga omurungo tawe, nabo abeene nabalunjifu."
  36,22,"Ne khulwa shina ndalalaama ulia wanoonga tawe, ne ewuwe niwamulikalusibwa."
  36,23,"Koo, endiile abanyasaye bandi balali Ye tawe? Nyasaye Omunji wetsimbabaasi niyanyenyela amabii, okhusaba khwenyu shikhulaakhoonya shiosishiosi tawe, nohomba shibakhahabina tawe."
  36,24,"Toto mana esie endio emba endi mubukori bwa habulafu."
  36,25,"Toto esie esuubiile khu Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, kho rechelesie.”"
  36,26,"Naboolelwa mbu: “Injila mumukunda kwomwikulu.” Naboola mbu: “Abayie abandu banje bamanyanga khwo."
  36,27,"Shingala Nyasaye wanje Omulesi yandesheele mana niyanda mubalia abahelesibwa oluyali.”"